,"id":189275,"idMal":61335,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":83,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774110600,"episode":9,"timeUntilAiring":491871},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/189275","startDate":{"day":25,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Medalist Season 2","native":"メダリスト 第2期","romaji":"Medalist 2nd Season","userPreferred":"Medalist 2nd Season"},"trailer":{"id":"GTaqXo7scOY","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/GTaqXo7scOY/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-112929},{"airingAt":1773503760,"episode":10,"id":404726,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/187989-ELfQpRahhT3L.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#d6a178","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx187989-IjVYJxi0bEcr.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx187989-IjVYJxi0bEcr.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx187989-IjVYJxi0bEcr.jpg"},"description":"In the mid-21st century, Tokyo's mafia can turn into ether-enhanced Demon Lords, and Braves hunt them down. Yashiro, the Grim Reaper, reluctantly takes a new apprentice named Aki Jogamine, a high school girl training to become a Brave. He soon finds himself dragged into one troublesome case after another. The supernatural story of a scumbag master and his self-proclaimed apprentice begins!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":23,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":24,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Comedy","Drama","Fantasy","Sci-Fi"],"id":187989,"idMal":61217,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":63,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774108560,"episode":11,"timeUntilAiring":489831},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/187989","startDate":{"day":11,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["ผู้กล้าสวะ","Pahlawan Sampah"],"title":{"english":"Scum of the Brave","native":"勇者のクズ","romaji":"Yuusha no Kuzu","userPreferred":"Yuusha no Kuzu"},"trailer":{"id":"Lh-0y-O7GIg","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Lh-0y-O7GIg/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-114969},{"airingAt":1773502200,"episode":23,"id":405660,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/187464-JRW0ASx02H83.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4bb43","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx187464-NJtK3VC54vPm.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx187464-NJtK3VC54vPm.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx187464-NJtK3VC54vPm.jpg"},"description":"Tanzaburo Tojima has dreamt of becoming a Kamen Rider his whole life. But now that he’s 40 years old, he’s starting to think his dream may never come true…until he’s swept up in a series of crimes inspired by the infamous “Shocker”! From Air Master and 81 Diver’s Shibata Yokusaru comes a wild, heartfelt tale about adults who love Kamen Rider a little too much and start playing pretend—for real!\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":24,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Comedy"],"id":187464,"idMal":61159,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":74,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774107000,"episode":24,"timeUntilAiring":488271},"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/187464","startDate":{"day":5,"month":10,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Tojima Tanzaburo Wants To Be A Masked Rider","โทจิมะอยากเป็นคาเมนไรเดอร์","토지마 탄자부로는 가면라이더가 되고 싶어"],"title":{"english":"Tojima Wants to Be a Kamen Rider","native":"東島丹三郎は仮面ライダーになりたい","romaji":"Toujima Tanzaburou wa Kamen Rider ni Naritai","userPreferred":"Toujima Tanzaburou wa Kamen Rider ni Naritai"},"trailer":{"id":"76c3cCV1BcU","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/76c3cCV1BcU/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-116529},{"airingAt":1773500400,"episode":21,"id":409965,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/185116-eQ55D57Wj1oJ.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#43aee4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx185116-DIFRjiMgz1IS.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx185116-DIFRjiMgz1IS.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx185116-DIFRjiMgz1IS.jpg"},"description":"The story of \u003ci\u003eGNOSIA\u003c/i\u003e takes place on a ship drifting through space. Gnosia is an enemy that disguises itself as a human and attacks them. It is now on the spaceship, causing everyone onboard to be suspicious of each other. The crew decides to vote on the most suspicious-looking person every day and put them into a cold sleep.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nIf the humans succeed in putting Gnosia to sleep, they'll win. On the other hand, if they don't, everyone on board is in danger. The right decision must be made. No matter what decision is made by the main character, Yuri, she finds herself in a time loop that returns her to the first day of the crisis. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nWill the crew on board make the right decision? What is the secret behind the time loop? What secrets hide behind the faces of everyone on board?\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n\u003ci\u003eGNOSIA\u003c/i\u003e begins now – a story of looping, fleeting moments that feels like an eternity but passes by in an instant.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nHave a pleasant journey.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":25,"endDate":{"day":15,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":21,"format":"TV","genres":["Drama","Mystery","Sci-Fi","Thriller"],"id":185116,"idMal":60427,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":77,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/185116","startDate":{"day":12,"month":10,"year":2025},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"GNOSIA","native":"グノーシア","romaji":"Gnosia","userPreferred":"Gnosia"},"trailer":{"id":"Rm4ipMdFpeA","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Rm4ipMdFpeA/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-118329},{"airingAt":1773500400,"episode":10,"id":406138,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/198374-cnzGgIW2KzHr.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#4386ff","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx198374-ROZU3qJGX4uS.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx198374-ROZU3qJGX4uS.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx198374-ROZU3qJGX4uS.jpg"},"description":"After a traumatic incident ends his teaching career, Rei Hitoma is certain he hates humans. Yet when he sees a job for “a teacher who truly cares for their students,” he’s compelled to apply. Before he knows it, he’s hired—only to find out his students are demi-humans. What begins as a job becomes a journey for healing for both a teacher who’s lost faith in humanity and students who dream of it.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":5,"month":4,"year":2026},"episodes":13,"format":"TV","genres":["Comedy","Drama","Fantasy","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":198374,"idMal":62432,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":61,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774105200,"episode":11,"timeUntilAiring":486471},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/198374","startDate":{"day":11,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["ห้องเรียนต่างสายพันธุ์ ของอาจารย์ผู้เกลียดมนุษย์"],"title":{"english":"A Misanthrope Teaches a Class for Demi-Humans","native":"人外教室の人間嫌い教師","romaji":"Jingai Kyoushitsu no Ningengirai Kyoushi","userPreferred":"Jingai Kyoushitsu no Ningengirai Kyoushi"},"trailer":{"id":"rb0okw_1ExM","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/rb0okw_1ExM/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-118329},{"airingAt":1773500400,"episode":22,"id":405385,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"CN","coverImage":{"color":"#e45d5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx203953-0o0WnauWOeQO.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx203953-0o0WnauWOeQO.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx203953-0o0WnauWOeQO.jpg"},"description":"The third part of \u003ci\u003eMu Shen Ji\u003c/i\u003e.","duration":20,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":26,"format":"ONA","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy"],"id":203953,"idMal":null,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":86,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774105200,"episode":23,"timeUntilAiring":486471},"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/203953","startDate":{"day":19,"month":10,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Tales of Herding Gods 3","牧神记 叁"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"牧神记3","romaji":"Mu Shen Ji 3","userPreferred":"Mu Shen Ji 3"},"trailer":null,"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-118329},{"airingAt":1773499500,"episode":19,"id":408856,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/162669-SvOE44IccAT0.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1a150","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx162669-FLYUTftoXgMh.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx162669-FLYUTftoXgMh.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx162669-FLYUTftoXgMh.jpg"},"description":"\u003cb\u003eThe story of Fushi the immortal enters the modern era.\u003c/b\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nFollowing the battles in Renril, Fushi, like a tree, spreads his roots throughout the world, fighting to eliminate the Nokkers. Hundreds of years later, having completed his mission, he awakens in the modern era. He enjoys a life of peace, free of enemy threats and surrounded by precious friends, new and old. But ominous shadows grow near yet again. Enemies that enter into the fissures of the mind. And Fushi learns of the true goals of his creator, the Beholder.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nFaced with new trials, the time approaches for Fushi to make the ultimate decision.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: NHK PR, edited)","duration":25,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":22,"format":"TV","genres":["Adventure","Drama","Fantasy","Psychological","Supernatural"],"id":162669,"idMal":54703,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":76,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774104300,"episode":20,"timeUntilAiring":485571},"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/162669","startDate":{"day":4,"month":10,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"To Your Eternity Season 3","native":"不滅のあなたへ Season 3","romaji":"Fumetsu no Anata e Season 3","userPreferred":"Fumetsu no Anata e Season 3"},"trailer":{"id":"JmT51BjIJ5w","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/JmT51BjIJ5w/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-119229},{"airingAt":1773498600,"episode":11,"id":406886,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/166617-P4w3p0H4lE1O.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#1a1af1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx166617-34fpC9y47tTx.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx166617-34fpC9y47tTx.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx166617-34fpC9y47tTx.png"},"description":"In a Holy Grail War, Mages (Masters) and their Heroic Spirits (Servants) fight for the control of the Holy Grail—an omnipotent wish-granting device said to fulfill any desire. Years have passed since the end of the Fifth Holy Grail War in Japan. Now, signs portend the emergence of a new Holy Grail in the western American city of Snowfield. Sure enough, Masters and Servants begin to gather... \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nA missing Servant class...\u003cbr\u003e\nImpossible Servant summonings...\u003cbr\u003e\nA nation shrouded in secrecy...\u003cbr\u003e\nAnd a city created as a battleground.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nIn the face of such irregularities, the Holy Grail War is twisted and driven into the depth of madness. Let the curtain rise on a masquerade of humans and heroes, made to dance upon the stage of a false Holy Grail. \u003ci\u003eThis is a Holy Grail War covered in lies.\u003c/i\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Official Site, Aniplex USA, edited)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNotes:\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n•  \u003ci\u003eSpecial premiere of Episode 1 in its English Dub occurred in Los Angeles at the Fate 20th Anniversary Showcase event and as well through Crunchyroll’s YouTube Channel on November 23, 2024 before the Japanese television premiere.\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n•  \u003ci\u003eThe Japanese advanced premiere occurred during the \"Fate New Year's Eve TV Special 2024\" on December 31, 2024.\u003c/i\u003e","duration":25,"endDate":{"day":28,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":13,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy","Mystery","Supernatural"],"id":166617,"idMal":55830,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":83,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774103400,"episode":12,"timeUntilAiring":484671},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/166617","startDate":{"day":3,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Судьба/Странная подделка"],"title":{"english":"Fate/strange Fake","native":"Fate/strange Fake","romaji":"Fate/strange Fake","userPreferred":"Fate/strange Fake"},"trailer":{"id":"k1G8EvZg_BY","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/k1G8EvZg_BY/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-120129},{"airingAt":1773498600,"episode":10,"id":405106,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/187901-03I5T8QVX1FG.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#35bbf1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx187901-T91HmZAaNwOF.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx187901-T91HmZAaNwOF.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx187901-T91HmZAaNwOF.jpg"},"description":"Always ready for a fight! Destruction for destruction’s sake! The online streamer Aoringo is a troll, making the worst of the worst of boundary-pushing flamebait content and raking in the revenue from the hate-watchers. You may think he’s nothing more than a bottom feeder and a drain on society, but in reality, he’s high school dropout Souji Enishiro, a caring older brother with a sweet tooth who loves nothing more than his little sister. His viral videos? Just a way to pay his sister’s medical bills. And even if all of humanity hates him, he doesn’t care, so long as his little sister gets better. But then, something very strange begins to happen...\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":28,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Supernatural"],"id":187901,"idMal":61196,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":62,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774103400,"episode":11,"timeUntilAiring":484671},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/187901","startDate":{"day":10,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["デドアカ","เดดแอ็กเคานต์ พิฆาตบัญชีมรณะ"],"title":{"english":"Dead Account","native":"デッドアカウント","romaji":"Dead Account","userPreferred":"Dead Account"},"trailer":{"id":"ynnk0CIyu10","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ynnk0CIyu10/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-120129},{"airingAt":1773496800,"episode":10,"id":404750,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/163144-e6vGlARSvwyE.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4bb50","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx163144-XdVwFRxPGY6j.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx163144-XdVwFRxPGY6j.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx163144-XdVwFRxPGY6j.jpg"},"description":"Sequel season to \u003ci\u003eTRIGUN STAMPEDE\u003c/i\u003e.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nIt’s been two and a half years since the Lost JuLai tragedy, which laid waste to an entire city and engulfed the whole planet in chaos. Meryl, now a senior journalist, continues her search for Vash with her new younger sidekick, Milly, and runs into Wolfwood along the way. As plant robberies begin taking place once again, they sense Millions Knives’s organization conspiring behind the scenes.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nMeanwhile, Vash has taken the new name Eriks and is living in hiding in a backwater town when he gets an abrupt visit from Jessica, a young girl with an SOS from the third ship they call home. He thus decides to put an end to a long-standing feud in order to protect those dear to him.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nJust as the pieces of the story begin falling back together again, the planet receives a message from the far reaches of outer space: “We are a fleet of colony ships from Earth... Those who wish may accompany us to a new frontier.” The entire population rejoices at this news. However, as if to mock their celebration, the one-winged angel returns to wreak havoc and despair. Fates collide to forge a final conclusion for the panicked planet.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":28,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Comedy","Drama","Sci-Fi"],"id":163144,"idMal":54863,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":71,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774101600,"episode":11,"timeUntilAiring":482871},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/163144","startDate":{"day":10,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["トライガン スタンピード 完結編","TRIGUN STAMPEDE: Kanketsu-hen","トライガン スターゲイズ"],"title":{"english":"TRIGUN STARGAZE","native":"TRIGUN STARGAZE","romaji":"TRIGUN STARGAZE","userPreferred":"TRIGUN STARGAZE"},"trailer":{"id":"JBYLkW--zmI","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/JBYLkW--zmI/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-121929},{"airingAt":1773493200,"episode":11,"id":405075,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#4393c9","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx199446-2jYnGrTItjyu.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx199446-2jYnGrTItjyu.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx199446-2jYnGrTItjyu.jpg"},"description":"The story of Saioshi no Gikei Mederutame, Nagaikishimasu! follows the struggle of a player to protect his favorite character, who gets reincarnated as his older brother-in-law in a simulation raising game - however, the player is reincarnated as the younger brother who was meant to die.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: ANN)","duration":4,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV_SHORT","genres":["Fantasy","Romance"],"id":199446,"idMal":61969,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":51,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774098000,"episode":12,"timeUntilAiring":479271},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/199446","startDate":{"day":3,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["I’ll Live A Long Life to Adore My Absolute Fave—Currently My Stepbrother"],"title":{"english":"I'll Live a Long Life to Dote on My Favorite Stepbrother!","native":"最推しの義兄を愛でるため、長生きします！","romaji":"Saioshi no Gikei Mederu Tame, Nagaikishimasu!","userPreferred":"Saioshi no Gikei Mederu Tame, Nagaikishimasu!"},"trailer":{"id":"kH6Yrpboous","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/kH6Yrpboous/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-125529},{"airingAt":1773491400,"episode":10,"id":406966,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4505d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx202419-BmPPSzsegbcv.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx202419-BmPPSzsegbcv.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx202419-BmPPSzsegbcv.png"},"description":"Light anime for \u003ci\u003eOmae wa Mada Gunma wo Shiranai\u003c/i\u003e.","duration":6,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV_SHORT","genres":["Comedy"],"id":202419,"idMal":62864,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":46,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774096200,"episode":11,"timeUntilAiring":477471},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/202419","startDate":{"day":10,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["You Don't Know Gunma Yet"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"お前はまだグンマを知らない～令和版～ ","romaji":"Omae wa Mada Gunma wo Shiranai: Reiwa-ban","userPreferred":"Omae wa Mada Gunma wo Shiranai: Reiwa-ban"},"trailer":{"id":"O5_4AGv44sU","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/O5_4AGv44sU/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-127329},{"airingAt":1773491400,"episode":10,"id":405275,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/187941-wdkhGnf4LUH0.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1930d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx187941-ykmc8WRedPpw.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx187941-ykmc8WRedPpw.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx187941-ykmc8WRedPpw.jpg"},"description":"Our hero needs to come out of his shell... literally! Reborn in another world inside a dragon egg, he doesn’t have the amazing magic or mighty physical strength of your typical isekai’d adventurer just yet. He’ll need to break free and grow from a weak hatchling and into a fearsome beast if he wants to escape the deep, dark forest unscathed. What battles and adventures await him in this unique take on the isekai phenomenon?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: HIDIVE)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy"],"id":187941,"idMal":61207,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":62,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774096200,"episode":11,"timeUntilAiring":477471},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/187941","startDate":{"day":10,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["DoraTama"],"title":{"english":"Reincarnated as a Dragon Hatchling","native":"転生したらドラゴンの卵だった","romaji":"Tensei Shitara Dragon no Tamago Datta","userPreferred":"Tensei Shitara Dragon no Tamago Datta"},"trailer":{"id":"VPLmZd3ByAM","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/VPLmZd3ByAM/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-127329},{"airingAt":1773480300,"episode":19,"id":404837,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4bb5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx186736-zYDrRDuC55s5.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx186736-zYDrRDuC55s5.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx186736-zYDrRDuC55s5.png"},"description":"The second season of \u003ci\u003eKagaku×Bouken Survival!\u003c/i\u003e","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV","genres":[],"id":186736,"idMal":60983,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":48,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774085100,"episode":20,"timeUntilAiring":466371},"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/186736","startDate":{"day":4,"month":10,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":null,"native":"科学×冒険サバイバル！ 第2シリーズ","romaji":"Kagaku×Bouken Survival! 2nd Season","userPreferred":"Kagaku×Bouken Survival! 2nd Season"},"trailer":null,"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-138429},{"airingAt":1773478800,"episode":1193,"id":409738,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/235-MTmiz0uB0fMd.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#28a1e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx235-MyYT7K3chBdO.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx235-MyYT7K3chBdO.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx235-MyYT7K3chBdO.jpg"},"description":"Kudo Shinichi is a seventeen year-old high school detective whom people call the \"Modern Sherlock Holmes.\" However, one night after a date with his childhood sweetheart, Ran, Shinichi witnessed an illegal trade and, caught off his guard, was knocked unconscious and fed a drug that was supposed to kill him... but he woke up and found himself shrunken to a seven year-old. In order to track down the men who did this to him, Shinichi hid his identity and lived with Ran, whose father happened to be a hopeless detective, and with that came a series of murders and mysteries that he must solve. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Anime News Network)\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ci\u003eNote:\u003cbr\u003e\n- Includes Keisatsu Gakkou-hen - Wild Police Story in episodes 1029, 1038, 1042, 1061\u003cbr\u003e\n- Episodes 11, 52, 76, 118, 162, 184, 208, 342, 356, 449, 452, 487, 488, 489, 490, 515, 516, 521, 522, 651, 734, 804, 805, 927, 928, 1187 aired with a runtime of ~50 minutes as opposed to the standard 25 minute long episode.\u003cbr\u003e\n- Episodes 96, 129, 174, 219, 263, 304, 383, 479 aired with a runtime of ~90 minutes as opposed to the standard 25 minute long episode.\u003cbr\u003e\n- Episode 345, 425 aired with a runtime of ~115 minutes as opposed to the standard 25 minute long episode.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c/i\u003e","duration":25,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV","genres":["Adventure","Comedy","Mystery","Psychological"],"id":235,"idMal":235,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":82,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774083600,"episode":1194,"timeUntilAiring":464871},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/235","startDate":{"day":8,"month":1,"year":1996},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Detective Conan","Detectiu Conan","הבלש קונאן","Detektyw Conan","المحقق كونان","名侦探柯南","Meitantei Conan: Keisaku Gakkou Hen - Wild Police Story","名探偵コナン 警察学校編 Wild Police Story","Détective Conan","ยอดนักสืบจิ๋วโคนัน","Thám Tử Lừng Danh Conan","Detektiv Conan"],"title":{"english":"Case Closed","native":"名探偵コナン","romaji":"Meitantei Conan","userPreferred":"Meitantei Conan"},"trailer":null,"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-139929},{"airingAt":1773477000,"episode":12,"id":406911,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#50bbe4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx189258-qhtrra5ebBm6.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx189258-qhtrra5ebBm6.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx189258-qhtrra5ebBm6.jpg"},"description":"The second season of \u003ci\u003eAo no Miburo\u003c/i\u003e.","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV","genres":["Drama"],"id":189258,"idMal":61333,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":65,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/189258","startDate":{"day":20,"month":12,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Ao no Miburo Season 2"],"title":{"english":"Blue Miburo Season 2","native":"青のミブロ 芹沢暗殺編","romaji":"Ao no Miburo: Serizawa Ansatsu-hen","userPreferred":"Ao no Miburo: Serizawa Ansatsu-hen"},"trailer":{"id":"7hWWDxF0hyo","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/7hWWDxF0hyo/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-141729},{"airingAt":1773475200,"episode":906,"id":380034,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/8687-aa3QbJjGfy3B.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#fed628","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b8687-bBnJMGnih4PT.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b8687-bBnJMGnih4PT.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/b8687-bBnJMGnih4PT.jpg"},"description":"A new Doraemon series produced by the same team as the 1979 series (in association with Studio Pierrot) with new voice actors and staff and updated character designs.","duration":25,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV","genres":["Adventure","Comedy","Sci-Fi"],"id":8687,"idMal":8687,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":77,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774080000,"episode":907,"timeUntilAiring":461271},"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/8687","startDate":{"day":15,"month":4,"year":2005},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":null,"native":"ドラえもん (2005)","romaji":"Doraemon (2005)","userPreferred":"Doraemon (2005)"},"trailer":null,"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-143529},{"airingAt":1773473400,"episode":1326,"id":409411,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/966-J5CwLLTBs4OO.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4e428","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b966-QUCdKAk4ls9J.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b966-QUCdKAk4ls9J.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/b966-QUCdKAk4ls9J.jpg"},"description":"Crayon Shin-chan follows the wacky antics and adventures of five-year-old Shinnosuke \"Shin\" Nohara and his parents, neighbors, and friends and is set in Kasukabe, Saitama Prefecture, Japan.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nMany of the jokes in the series stem from Shin-chan's occasionally weird, unnatural and inappropriate use of language, as well as from his inappropriate behavior. A typical gag involves Shin-chan confounding his parents by using the wrong phrase for the occasion; for example, saying \"Welcome back!\" instead of \"I am back!\" when he comes home.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nDuring the beginning of the series, the TV show was mostly based on the storyline in the original manga. As the show progressed, more and more episodes became anime-original.","duration":21,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV","genres":["Comedy","Ecchi","Slice of Life"],"id":966,"idMal":966,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":78,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774078200,"episode":1327,"timeUntilAiring":459471},"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/966","startDate":{"day":13,"month":4,"year":1992},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Shin Chan","native":"クレヨンしんちゃん","romaji":"Crayon Shin-chan","userPreferred":"Crayon Shin-chan"},"trailer":null,"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-145329},{"airingAt":1773453600,"episode":144,"id":408244,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"CN","coverImage":{"color":"#5daee4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx137683-IMuvIECdZNBh.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx137683-IMuvIECdZNBh.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx137683-IMuvIECdZNBh.png"},"description":"The Tang Sect in a turbulent world. There is nothing but martial spirit here. Ten thousand years after the founding of the Tang Sect, it is in relative decline. An extremely talented man was born. Can the new Shrek Seven Monsters revive the Tang Sect and bring it back to glory? A soul beast of over one million years old; Electrolux who can pick stars; The new soul utensil system that led to the decline of the Tang Sect... A lot of secrets are to be revealed. Can the secret weapons of the Tang Sect be sharp again? Can the Tang Sect regain its former glory?\n\u003c/br\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\n(Source: WeTV)","duration":20,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":156,"format":"ONA","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy","Romance"],"id":137683,"idMal":51836,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":81,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774058400,"episode":145,"timeUntilAiring":439671},"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/137683","startDate":{"day":24,"month":6,"year":2023},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Soul Land 2: The Unrivaled Tang Sect","斗罗大陆Ⅱ绝世唐门","Soul Land 2: Peerless Tang Sect"],"title":{"english":"Soul Land 2: The Peerless Tang Clan","native":"斗罗大陆2绝世唐门","romaji":"Douluo Dalu 2: Jueshi Tangmen","userPreferred":"Douluo Dalu 2: Jueshi Tangmen"},"trailer":null,"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-165129},{"airingAt":1773442800,"episode":8,"id":409607,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#4393e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx203296-LYXWSdP4N4YF.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx203296-LYXWSdP4N4YF.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx203296-LYXWSdP4N4YF.jpg"},"description":"The fifth season of \u003ci\u003eCardfight!! Vanguard: Divinez.\u003c/i\u003e","duration":null,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy"],"id":203296,"idMal":62649,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":62,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774047600,"episode":9,"timeUntilAiring":428871},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/203296","startDate":{"day":10,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["CARDFIGHT!! VANGUARD Divinez Parallactic Clash"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"カードファイト!! ヴァンガード Divinez 幻真星戦編","romaji":"Cardfight!! Vanguard: Divinez Genma Seisen-hen","userPreferred":"Cardfight!! Vanguard: Divinez Genma Seisen-hen"},"trailer":null,"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-175929},{"airingAt":1773441000,"episode":207,"id":406438,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1bb43","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx142274-qPfkeKk4caKI.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx142274-qPfkeKk4caKI.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx142274-qPfkeKk4caKI.png"},"description":"The year is 20XX. The ninja, who once forged the history of Japan, were scattered across the country during the Meiji Restoration. As these ninja mingled with the other clans, their bloodline thinned, and they gradually faded from sight. The descendants of these ninja clans, seeking to preserve their heritage, formed the WNA (World Ninja Association) in the hope of carrying on their legacy.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nAnd so it was that the WNA succeeded in developing Ninja-Gum, an art which could summon forth the strength of the Shinobi. And yet creating the most powerful Ninja-Gum requires the strongest of ninja DNA. So it was that the Ninjala Tournament was held, that the mightiest of all ninjas could be found...\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Official Game website)","duration":23,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Comedy","Sci-Fi"],"id":142274,"idMal":50418,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":49,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774045800,"episode"