erred":"Jigokuraku 2nd Season"},"trailer":{"id":"JLe_NUnAZVs","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/JLe_NUnAZVs/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-32951},{"airingAt":1773585000,"episode":9,"id":409503,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#d65d1a","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx187062-JuXPEjrLQSeO.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx187062-JuXPEjrLQSeO.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx187062-JuXPEjrLQSeO.png"},"description":"The fire extinguishing samurai who stopped the great fire was called \"The fire-eating bird\". Matsunaga Gengo, once known as the \"Fire-eating Bird\", was the best fire-fighting samurai in Edo. He had resigned from the fire brigade for a reason but suddenly received an invitation to serve in the Shinjo clan.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e \n\nThe Shinjo clan's fire-fighting team had no money and no personnel and was looked down upon by those around them. With the encouragement of his wife, Miyuki, Gengo decides to rebuild the collapsed fire-fighting clan as its chairman. Gengo and his friends, all of whom have their own peculiarities, struggle to \"save any life\", despite being ridiculed as \"ragged steeplejacks\"(= the 'Boro-Tobi-Gumi'.), In Edo, a mysterious series of suspicious fires called \"foxfires\" continue.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nAn entertaining action drama opens, with the firefighters scrambling to save lives in the face of the approaching disaster!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Amuse Creative Studio)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Drama"],"id":187062,"idMal":61084,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":42,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774189800,"episode":10,"timeUntilAiring":571009},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/187062","startDate":{"day":11,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["วิหคกินเพลิง: หน่วยพิทักษ์เพลิงแห่งเอโดะ"],"title":{"english":"Oedo Fire Slayer -The Legend of Phoenix-","native":"火喰鳥","romaji":"Hikuidori","userPreferred":"Hikuidori"},"trailer":{"id":"bB6qXk2YOYE","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/bB6qXk2YOYE/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-33791},{"airingAt":1773583200,"episode":10,"id":404604,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/195518-IpfwJgnWa6nD.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#5d86e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx195518-XXcYHi6tXM6v.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx195518-XXcYHi6tXM6v.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx195518-XXcYHi6tXM6v.jpg"},"description":"Tiararose Lapis Clamentile is set to marry Hartknights, crown prince of Lapis Lazuli—until she suddenly remembers her past life and realizes she’s been reincarnated into her favorite game, The Ring of Lapis Lazuli, as the doomed villainess! But just as she’s about to lose hope, the crown prince of Aquasteed proposes instead. Could this unexpected turn finally lead to a happy ending of her own?\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":29,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Fantasy","Romance"],"id":195518,"idMal":62000,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":58,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774188000,"episode":11,"timeUntilAiring":569209},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/195518","startDate":{"day":11,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["The Villainess Is Being Doted on by the Crown Prince of the Neighboring Country","ท่านหญิงนางร้ายถูกเจ้าชายรัชทายาท ของอาณาจักรข้างเคียงหลงรัก"],"title":{"english":"The Villainess Is Adored by the Prince of the Neighbor Kingdom","native":"悪役令嬢は隣国の王太子に溺愛される","romaji":"Akuyaku Reijou wa Ringoku no Outaishi ni Dekiai Sareru","userPreferred":"Akuyaku Reijou wa Ringoku no Outaishi ni Dekiai Sareru"},"trailer":{"id":"3wNyyhzLqA0","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/3wNyyhzLqA0/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-35591},{"airingAt":1773579600,"episode":12,"id":408494,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/186333-JN8lx2aNOTg1.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#5da1e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx186333-32qDHxLkndpg.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx186333-32qDHxLkndpg.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx186333-32qDHxLkndpg.png"},"description":"Kunon, a young man who cannot see, has the goal of creating new eyes with water magic. After just five months of learning sorcery, Kunon surpassed his own mentor and honed his talent as he tried to do a feat that's never been done before. A fantasy about a young man, a blind genius, who opens up the world through curiosity in the pursuit for magic is about to begin.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":22,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":13,"format":"ONA","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy"],"id":186333,"idMal":60810,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":64,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774184400,"episode":13,"timeUntilAiring":565609},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/186333","startDate":{"day":4,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["จอมเวทผู้มองเห็นทุกสิ่ง คุนอน"],"title":{"english":"Kunon the Sorcerer Can See","native":"魔術師クノンは見えている","romaji":"Majutsushi Kunon wa Mieteiru","userPreferred":"Majutsushi Kunon wa Mieteiru"},"trailer":{"id":"8AdpUgiFs2o","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/8AdpUgiFs2o/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-39191},{"airingAt":1773577800,"episode":12,"id":406734,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#fff193","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx177580-ujQw6Ws3oVCi.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx177580-ujQw6Ws3oVCi.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx177580-ujQw6Ws3oVCi.jpg"},"description":"Mizuki Ashiya is on a mission: disguise herself as a boy and enroll in a male boarding school to meet her idol, high jump star Izumi Sano. But after successfully infiltrating the school, she discovers he’s suddenly quit the sport! Now Mizuki must dodge suspicion, protect her cover, and somehow reach the boy she came all this way for—all while surviving the chaos of an all-boys dorm!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":15,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":12,"format":"ONA","genres":["Comedy","Drama","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":177580,"idMal":58861,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":67,"nextAiringEpisode":null,"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/177580","startDate":{"day":4,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"FINISHED","synonyms":["Hana-Kimi: For You in Full Blossom","สับขั้วมาลุ้นรัก"],"title":{"english":"Hana-Kimi","native":"花ざかりの君たちへ","romaji":"Hanazakari no Kimitachi e","userPreferred":"Hanazakari no Kimitachi e"},"trailer":{"id":"CemNP0vIiJI","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/CemNP0vIiJI/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-40991},{"airingAt":1773567000,"episode":2823,"id":394963,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/2406-ROqXxejQ5bH9.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1bb43","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx2406-nP8NIct9Sci3.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx2406-nP8NIct9Sci3.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx2406-nP8NIct9Sci3.jpg"},"description":"The main character is a mother named Sazae-san. She lives in a house with her husband, her kid, her siblings and her parents. The show is the ultimate family program and tends to follow traditional themes. Think of this show as the Japanese equivalent to \"The Partridge Family\" and you'll get a good feel for this show's atmosphere. Don't expect to see things like violence, swearing, kung-fu action or magical girls. The plots are more like \"Today, Sazae-san goes to the new mall and gets lost\". Such \"boring\" plotlines and the simplistic art are often a turn-off to non-Japanese audiences, but most Japanese find the show incredibly good. As a result, it continues to be one of the top ratings grabbers on TV and is one of the few anime that is considered \"acceptable\" by adults.","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV","genres":["Comedy","Slice of Life"],"id":2406,"idMal":2406,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":58,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774171800,"episode":2824,"timeUntilAiring":553009},"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/2406","startDate":{"day":5,"month":10,"year":1969},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Mrs. Sazae"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"サザエさん","romaji":"Sazae-san","userPreferred":"Sazae-san"},"trailer":null,"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-51791},{"airingAt":1773565200,"episode":357,"id":408745,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/118123-BvHyzWd850nZ.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4ae5d","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx118123-xqn5fYsjKXJU.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx118123-xqn5fYsjKXJU.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx118123-xqn5fYsjKXJU.png"},"description":"From unraveling the secrets of opening and closing doors to defusing surprise packages more commonly known as bombs, there is never a dull day at the Hololive Production office! \u003ci\u003eHolo no Graffiti\u003c/i\u003e follows an eccentric cast of Virtual YouTubers, also known as \"VTubers,\" going about their absurd yet hilarious daily lives, detailing all their cute moments and mishaps.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: MAL Rewrite)","duration":2,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"ONA","genres":["Action","Adventure","Comedy"],"id":118123,"idMal":44042,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":79,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774170000,"episode":358,"timeUntilAiring":551209},"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/118123","startDate":{"day":5,"month":5,"year":2019},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Hologra 3D Short Animation","Hologra","ホロぐら","Hololive","הולולייב"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"ホロのぐらふぃてぃ","romaji":"Holo no Graffiti","userPreferred":"Holo no Graffiti"},"trailer":null,"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-53591},{"airingAt":1773563400,"episode":10,"id":404134,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/183660-RmcBY27wn8A4.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f15d35","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx183660-B6o9cMfSfScX.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx183660-B6o9cMfSfScX.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx183660-B6o9cMfSfScX.jpg"},"description":"Kaya-chan attends Hanamugi Kindergarten, and she has an incredibly strong sixth sense. She secretly beats up the ghosts that stalk her friends and family, but in turn, she’s treated like a troublemaker since nobody understands her strange behavior. Everything changes when her teacher, Chie, discovers her secret. Kaya-chan's fists will go flying at any sinister spirits that show up!\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":29,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Comedy","Horror","Slice of Life"],"id":183660,"idMal":60223,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":70,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774168200,"episode":11,"timeUntilAiring":549409},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/183660","startDate":{"day":11,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["カヤコワ","KayaKowa","คายะจังไม่กลัวหรอกนะ"],"title":{"english":"Kaya-chan Isn't Scary","native":"カヤちゃんはコワくない","romaji":"Kaya-chan wa Kowakunai","userPreferred":"Kaya-chan wa Kowakunai"},"trailer":{"id":"un9g38-wbHw","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/un9g38-wbHw/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-55391},{"airingAt":1773561600,"episode":10,"id":403927,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/184951-Rx1mZZfKa9IU.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1ae28","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx184951-s8Lg2muPBhdX.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx184951-s8Lg2muPBhdX.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx184951-s8Lg2muPBhdX.jpg"},"description":"Suzuki’s a high school girl in love, but the guy she’s fallen for is nothing like her! While she’s cheerful, outgoing, and always trying to fit in, her classmate Yusuke Tani is stoic, quiet, and doesn’t seem to care what people think of him. Will Suzuki be able to overcome her anxieties and ask him out, or will she discover that opposites really don’t attract?\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":29,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Comedy","Drama","Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":184951,"idMal":60371,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":82,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774166400,"episode":11,"timeUntilAiring":547609},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/184951","startDate":{"day":11,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["ลุ้นรักฉบับคู่ต่างขั้ว","정반대의 너와 나"],"title":{"english":"You and I Are Polar Opposites","native":"正反対な君と僕","romaji":"Seihantai na Kimi to Boku","userPreferred":"Seihantai na Kimi to Boku"},"trailer":{"id":"b5vpRUDkhT0","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/b5vpRUDkhT0/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-57191},{"airingAt":1773559800,"episode":10,"id":404640,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/192507-nv0NJmhQYTgz.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#5086e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx192507-SCmImUlUnpAD.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx192507-SCmImUlUnpAD.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx192507-SCmImUlUnpAD.jpg"},"description":"Yoi Takiguchi has long legs, a deep voice, and a handsome face…in other words, Yoi is such a good-looking guy that most people don’t notice or care that she is, in fact, a girl. Indeed, she’s had the nickname “Prince” for as long as she can remember. That is, until she met Ichimura-senpai…the only person who really seemed to see her for herself. To her surprise, she’s not sure how to handle this new relationship, especially when her newfound friend is a prince himself (and a guy prince, at that). The story of the two high school princes starts here!\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":29,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":12,"format":"TV","genres":["Romance","Slice of Life"],"id":192507,"idMal":61663,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":73,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774164600,"episode":11,"timeUntilAiring":545809},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/192507","startDate":