Gaze","native":"光阴之外","romaji":"Guangyin Zhi Wai","userPreferred":"Guangyin Zhi Wai"},"trailer":{"id":"o08Ry50zwrE","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/o08Ry50zwrE/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-78791},{"airingAt":1773534600,"episode":22,"id":410433,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/196553-RfPJobQ0VMkf.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":null,"extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx196553-9whoPCB5gyKB.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx196553-9whoPCB5gyKB.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx196553-9whoPCB5gyKB.jpg"},"description":"SI-VIS is a co-ed music group, led by Yosuke, shaking up the global music scene with their unmatched vocals and performances. However, they are actually heroes in disguise, battling against mysterious forces threatening the world. They convert audience energy at live performances into combat power. Luckily, the battles appear to be ordinary concerts to the public, keeping their identity a secret.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n (Source: Crunchyroll)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":29,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":24,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Music","Sci-Fi"],"id":196553,"idMal":62126,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":57,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774139400,"episode":23,"timeUntilAiring":520609},"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/196553","startDate":{"day":5,"month":10,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["シーヴィス"],"title":{"english":"SI-VIS: The Sound of Heroes","native":"SI-VIS: The Sound of Heroes","romaji":"SI-VIS: The Sound of Heroes","userPreferred":"SI-VIS: The Sound of Heroes"},"trailer":{"id":"ssg6MbJ9Ejo","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/ssg6MbJ9Ejo/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-84191},{"airingAt":1773534600,"episode":49,"id":405931,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f15df1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx184470-m2izEvBeO49C.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx184470-m2izEvBeO49C.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx184470-m2izEvBeO49C.jpg"},"description":"It's a new semester! Himari and Mitsuki have become second-year students of Paradise Private Academy! Their school lives become more and more lively with the introduction of new underclassmen full of individuality and personality.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nIn the AiPri-Verse, new AiPri are appearing one after another! Everyone tries their hand at a brand new, never-before-seen Buzzrium Change! In the midst of all this, the mysterious Princess Ring Clover and her butler, Shimitsuu, are holding an Aipri contest. They say the winner will become an admired \"Eternal Aipri.\" Himari and Mitsuki are all ready and full of fighting spirit! But it appears Princess Ring holds a very large secret...\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nAs their friends increase, so does the mysteries of the ring. The Ring arc finally begins!\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Offiical Website, translated)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV","genres":["Music","Slice of Life"],"id":184470,"idMal":61092,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":70,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774139400,"episode":50,"timeUntilAiring":520609},"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/184470","startDate":{"day":6,"month":4,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["ひみつのアイプリ 2期","Himitsu no AiPri 2nd Season"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"ひみつのアイプリ リング編","romaji":"Himitsu no AiPri: Ring-hen","userPreferred":"Himitsu no AiPri: Ring-hen"},"trailer":{"id":"aM7Q-sCzy8A","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/aM7Q-sCzy8A/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-84191},{"airingAt":1773532800,"episode":22,"id":410346,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/188388-kCSxLPMY2JkD.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#fec928","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx188388-aXx9fsnvezBf.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx188388-aXx9fsnvezBf.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx188388-aXx9fsnvezBf.jpg"},"description":"\u003ci\u003eGLITCH THE FUTURE.\u003c/i\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\nTomoro Tenma lives in a world where human thoughts and emotions—known as “e-Pulse”—power AI devices called Sapotama. But when Digimon begin materializing from Sapotama and feeding on e-Pulse, society begins to fracture. After Gekkomon appears from his device, Tomoro joins Glowing Dawn, a secret team investigating rogue Digimon and the dark truth of a system both fueled and corrupted by emotion. What new future will be forged by humans and Digimon? \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n(Source: Crunchyroll, DIGIMON BEATBREAK Official Site, edited)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy","Sci-Fi"],"id":188388,"idMal":61269,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":69,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774137600,"episode":23,"timeUntilAiring":518809},"season":"FALL","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/188388","startDate":{"day":5,"month":10,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["デジモンビートブレイク","ดิจิมอน บีตเบรก"],"title":{"english":"DIGIMON BEATBREAK","native":"DIGIMON BEATBREAK","romaji":"DIGIMON BEATBREAK","userPreferred":"DIGIMON BEATBREAK"},"trailer":{"id":"naNctHU5MQE","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/naNctHU5MQE/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-85991},{"airingAt":1773532800,"episode":46,"id":410021,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#1aa1e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx178052-igWygf0ZG1gl.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx178052-igWygf0ZG1gl.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx178052-igWygf0ZG1gl.jpg"},"description":"The anime takes place in Alicepia, which is a mysterious country that has existed since ancient times. The inhabitants of Alicepia, the Alicepians, are a fun-loving people, but one day mysterious monsters called Jamaock appeared to threaten the peace of Alicepia. The story follows a trio of \"princesses\" who never forget the song in their hearts, even when facing such danger and step up to save the day with the power of music. \u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\n(Source: Anime News Network, Crunchyroll News, edited)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":29,"month":3,"year":2026},"episodes":48,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Mahou Shoujo","Music"],"id":178052,"idMal":59078,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":67,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774137600,"episode":47,"timeUntilAiring":518809},"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/178052","startDate":{"day":6,"month":4,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Princession Orchestra","プリオケ","PriOrche"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"プリンセッション・オーケストラ","romaji":"Princess-Session Orchestra","userPreferred":"Princess-Session Orchestra"},"trailer":{"id":"KE2gJE29ewQ","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/KE2gJE29ewQ/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-85991},{"airingAt":1773531000,"episode":7,"id":407387,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/202957-B9U0hNv2Dqap.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#d6ae1a","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx202957-fxZGgJTvwXzP.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx202957-fxZGgJTvwXzP.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx202957-fxZGgJTvwXzP.jpg"},"description":" The 23rd installment of the long-running \u003ci\u003ePrecure\u003c/i\u003e series.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nAnna Akechi is a second-year junior high student living in Makoto Mirai Town. On her 14th birthday, she has a chance encounter with a fairy named Pochitan, and a magical pendant caused her to travel back in time from 2027 to 1999! In the Makoto Mirai Town 28 years in the past, Anna meets Mikuru Kobayashi, a girl her age who wants to become a great detective.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\nMeanwhile, people in town are in trouble as their prized possessions are being stolen from under their noses - the cause being a group of Phantom Thieves. To stop them, Anna and Mikuru turn into Precures! Maybe if they solve these mysteries, Anna can find her way back to her own time?\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Official Website, translated)","duration":24,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV","genres":["Mahou Shoujo","Mystery"],"id":202957,"idMal":63042,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":76,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774135800,"episode":8,"timeUntilAiring":517009},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/202957","startDate":{"day":1,"month":2,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["TanPre (たんプリ)"],"title":{"english":"Star Detective Precure!","native":"名探偵プリキュア！","romaji":"Meitantei Precure!","userPreferred":"Meitantei Precure!"},"trailer":{"id":"qjozo1fh7OI","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/qjozo1fh7OI/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-87791},{"airingAt":1773531000,"episode":9,"id":400082,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e47828","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx196227-B9kbcrGihskA.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx196227-B9kbcrGihskA.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx196227-B9kbcrGihskA.png"},"description":"After you fall asleep or while you're out, what are Tomica and Tom doing? Are they sleeping peacefully in the toy box? Are they just sitting there on the floor? Or maybe... No one knows the story of Tomica and Tom, but today we'll let you in on a special secret.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Official site)","duration":2,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV_SHORT","genres":["Slice of Life"],"id":196227,"idMal":62083,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":50,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1776555000,"episode":10,"timeUntilAiring":2936209},"season":"SUMMER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/196227","startDate":{"day":20,"month":7,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Tomica to Tom","Tomica and Tom"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"トミカとトム","romaji":"TOMICA \u0026 TOM","userPreferred":"TOMICA \u0026 TOM"},"trailer":{"id":"Lgj9wFPjmEw","site":"youtube","thumbnail":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Lgj9wFPjmEw/hqdefault.jpg"},"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-87791},{"airingAt":1773530880,"episode":50,"id":411202,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/185646-69FyAu3rfhEC.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#aed643","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx185646-2eGmsnaSHiLC.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx185646-2eGmsnaSHiLC.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx185646-2eGmsnaSHiLC.jpg"},"description":"The story of the series follows the everyday adventures of Koupen-chan and his friends as they enjoy the little things in life.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Crunchyroll News, edited)\n","duration":1,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"T