5)","userPreferred":"Doraemon (2005)"},"trailer":null,"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-143591},{"airingAt":1773473400,"episode":1326,"id":409411,"media":{"bannerImage":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/banner/966-J5CwLLTBs4OO.jpg","countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#e4e428","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b966-QUCdKAk4ls9J.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/b966-QUCdKAk4ls9J.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/b966-QUCdKAk4ls9J.jpg"},"description":"Crayon Shin-chan follows the wacky antics and adventures of five-year-old Shinnosuke \"Shin\" Nohara and his parents, neighbors, and friends and is set in Kasukabe, Saitama Prefecture, Japan.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nMany of the jokes in the series stem from Shin-chan's occasionally weird, unnatural and inappropriate use of language, as well as from his inappropriate behavior. A typical gag involves Shin-chan confounding his parents by using the wrong phrase for the occasion; for example, saying \"Welcome back!\" instead of \"I am back!\" when he comes home.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nDuring the beginning of the series, the TV show was mostly based on the storyline in the original manga. As the show progressed, more and more episodes became anime-original.","duration":21,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV","genres":["Comedy","Ecchi","Slice of Life"],"id":966,"idMal":966,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":78,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774078200,"episode":1327,"timeUntilAiring":459409},"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/966","startDate":{"day":13,"month":4,"year":1992},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Shin Chan","native":"クレヨンしんちゃん","romaji":"Crayon Shin-chan","userPreferred":"Crayon Shin-chan"},"trailer":null,"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-145391},{"airingAt":1773453600,"episode":144,"id":408244,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"CN","coverImage":{"color":"#5daee4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx137683-IMuvIECdZNBh.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx137683-IMuvIECdZNBh.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx137683-IMuvIECdZNBh.png"},"description":"The Tang Sect in a turbulent world. There is nothing but martial spirit here. Ten thousand years after the founding of the Tang Sect, it is in relative decline. An extremely talented man was born. Can the new Shrek Seven Monsters revive the Tang Sect and bring it back to glory? A soul beast of over one million years old; Electrolux who can pick stars; The new soul utensil system that led to the decline of the Tang Sect... A lot of secrets are to be revealed. Can the secret weapons of the Tang Sect be sharp again? Can the Tang Sect regain its former glory?\n\u003c/br\u003e\u003c/br\u003e\n(Source: WeTV)","duration":20,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":156,"format":"ONA","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy","Romance"],"id":137683,"idMal":51836,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":81,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774058400,"episode":145,"timeUntilAiring":439609},"season":null,"siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/137683","startDate":{"day":24,"month":6,"year":2023},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Soul Land 2: The Unrivaled Tang Sect","斗罗大陆Ⅱ绝世唐门","Soul Land 2: Peerless Tang Sect"],"title":{"english":"Soul Land 2: The Peerless Tang Clan","native":"斗罗大陆2绝世唐门","romaji":"Douluo Dalu 2: Jueshi Tangmen","userPreferred":"Douluo Dalu 2: Jueshi Tangmen"},"trailer":null,"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-165191},{"airingAt":1773442800,"episode":8,"id":409607,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#4393e4","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx203296-LYXWSdP4N4YF.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx203296-LYXWSdP4N4YF.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx203296-LYXWSdP4N4YF.jpg"},"description":"The fifth season of \u003ci\u003eCardfight!! Vanguard: Divinez.\u003c/i\u003e","duration":null,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Adventure","Fantasy"],"id":203296,"idMal":62649,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":62,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774047600,"episode":9,"timeUntilAiring":428809},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/203296","startDate":{"day":10,"month":1,"year":2026},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["CARDFIGHT!! VANGUARD Divinez Parallactic Clash"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"カードファイト!! ヴァンガード Divinez 幻真星戦編","romaji":"Cardfight!! Vanguard: Divinez Genma Seisen-hen","userPreferred":"Cardfight!! Vanguard: Divinez Genma Seisen-hen"},"trailer":null,"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-175991},{"airingAt":1773441000,"episode":207,"id":406438,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#f1bb43","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx142274-qPfkeKk4caKI.png","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx142274-qPfkeKk4caKI.png","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx142274-qPfkeKk4caKI.png"},"description":"The year is 20XX. The ninja, who once forged the history of Japan, were scattered across the country during the Meiji Restoration. As these ninja mingled with the other clans, their bloodline thinned, and they gradually faded from sight. The descendants of these ninja clans, seeking to preserve their heritage, formed the WNA (World Ninja Association) in the hope of carrying on their legacy.\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nAnd so it was that the WNA succeeded in developing Ninja-Gum, an art which could summon forth the strength of the Shinobi. And yet creating the most powerful Ninja-Gum requires the strongest of ninja DNA. So it was that the Ninjala Tournament was held, that the mightiest of all ninjas could be found...\n\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n(Source: Official Game website)","duration":23,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV","genres":["Action","Comedy","Sci-Fi"],"id":142274,"idMal":50418,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":49,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774045800,"episode":208,"timeUntilAiring":427009},"season":"WINTER","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/142274","startDate":{"day":8,"month":1,"year":2022},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":[],"title":{"english":"Ninjala the Animation","native":"ニンジャラ","romaji":"Ninjala","userPreferred":"Ninjala"},"trailer":null,"type":"ANIME"},"timeUntilAiring":-177791},{"airingAt":1773439200,"episode":49,"id":406264,"media":{"bannerImage":null,"countryOfOrigin":"JP","coverImage":{"color":"#5da1f1","extraLarge":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx184289-v85FJN0O4S1j.jpg","large":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/medium/bx184289-v85FJN0O4S1j.jpg","medium":"https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/small/bx184289-v85FJN0O4S1j.jpg"},"description":"Following the chaotic and heartwarming daily lives of Kaijuu who have come to Earth to conquer the world and live with their human masters.","duration":3,"endDate":{"day":null,"month":null,"year":null},"episodes":null,"format":"TV_SHORT","genres":["Slice of Life"],"id":184289,"idMal":60070,"isAdult":false,"meanScore":51,"nextAiringEpisode":{"airingAt":1774044000,"episode":50,"timeUntilAiring":425209},"season":"SPRING","siteUrl":"https://anilist.co/anime/184289","startDate":{"day":5,"month":4,"year":2025},"status":"RELEASING","synonyms":["Tiny Dragons Rule the World"],"title":{"english":null,"native":"かいじゅうせかいせいふく","romaji":"Kaijuu Sekai Seifuku","userPreferred":"Kaijuu Sekai Seifuku"},"trailer":{"id":"f8VXXMz6StQ","site":"you